{
  "stem": "23498.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But the wife didn't give him anything to eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She wanted-- she didn't have the heart to go to the Germans and say that he's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But on the other hand, she wanted him to die-- naturally die.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he was looking terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "When I saw him, I couldn't believe it's my-- I didn't recognize him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was a skeleton, a walking skeleton.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "What happened-- and Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Freund was a very nice man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He had our two fur coats, which he gave us right away when I came.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But he said, you know, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Yrena, ?] you have to take your brother, because-- I said, but it's-- it's-- we're all-- already liberated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You don't know what's going on here, they said.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You see, what happened-- my brother felt that it's-- that the Russians or whoever come here to liberate them, but they didn't tell him.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Because they didn't want the neighborhood to know that they hided a Jewish boy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "That was the main reason.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So my-- my brother was still hidden and treated the same way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "When-- you know, when the Russians were bombarding, he was on this-- not in the cellar, he was on the top.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he was so silly as me, making [POLISH], ham, and [POLISH], and other things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Because they have a pig-sty over there or whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He never tried anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he said he had rotten bread to eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he said that he wasn't hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he was happy, because he wasn't hungry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He knew that he will die.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So when-- but one thing, he was more free to go to the window.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And through the curtains, some people saw him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they called the Russians, mind you, because the Germans were gone.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
